On behalf of the children, volunteers, staff, and Board of Directors of Big Brothers Big Sisters,
please accept our appreciation for your donation supporting our annual "Bowl for Kids Sake"
event that was be held on February 27, 2010.
Your donation will help us continue to recruit, carefully screen, and match volunteer mentors with
the children and to provide them with on-going, professional support throughout the year. The
real impact of this event is that more kids in our area will feel better about themselves, do better in
school, get along better with others, and will keep away from drugs and alcohol!
With the continued support of generous companies and individuals such as yourself, we will
continue our mission to mentor and help our children so they grow into caring, compassionate
adults, who are able to make a positive difference in our community.
Once again, thank you for helping us make a BIG impact in our community.
Big Brothers Big Sisters of Greater Sacramento
